<p class="hero-sub">The operator guide to generating qualified gym leads in 2026, channel by channel, with real cost-per-lead benchmarks, and the AI-agent layer that converts 1.5-2x more of those leads into tour attendance. Built for gym owners, multi-unit operators, and franchisees.</p>
